OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773176766
OL,3,CTerms of reference for Pat Finucane
OL,4,Cinquiry published
OL,6,FThe terms of reference for an inquiry
OL,7,Finto the killing of Pat Finucane have
OL,8,Fbeen published by the Government.
OL,10,FMr Finucane, a human rights lawyer,
OL,11,Fwas shot dead at his family home in
OL,12,Fnorth Belfast by the loyalist
OL,13,Fparamilitary group the Ulster Defence
OL,14,FAssociation in February 1989, in an
OL,15,Fattack found by a series of
OL,16,Finvestigations to have involved
OL,17,Fcollusion with the state.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
