OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773176766
OL,3,CTerms of reference for Pat Finucane
OL,4,Cinquiry published
OL,6,FHis widow Geraldine, who was also
OL,7,Fwounded, and the couple's three
OL,8,Fchildren have been campaigning for
OL,9,Fdecades for a public inquiry to
OL,10,Festablish the extent of security force
OL,11,Finvolvement.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
