OL,3,CTerms of reference for Pat Finucane
OL,4,Cinquiry published
OL,6,FAccording to the terms of reference,
OL,7,Fthe inquiry's investigation will seek
OL,8,Fto determine the circumstances of Mr
OL,9,FFinucane's murder; to establish the
OL,10,Fidentity of all those involved in his
OL,11,Fmurder and the nature of their
OL,12,Finvolvement; to establish whether the
OL,13,Fevidence indicates that the murder
OL,14,Fcould have been prevented; and
OL,15,Finvestigate acts or omissions that are
OL,16,Frelevant to the murder.
OL,18,FAnnouncing the terms of reference on
OL,19,FMonday, Northern Ireland Secretary
OL,20,FHilary Benn said: "This was a barbaric
OL,21,Fand heinous crime.
OL,26,@|D@SOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
