PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773176766
OL,3,CTerms of reference for Pat Finucane
OL,4,Cinquiry published
OL,6,F"I commend the tireless campaign of
OL,7,FMrs Finucane and her family over the
OL,8,Fcourse of 37 years in seeking answers
OL,9,Fabout the brutal murder of their loved
OL,10,Fone, and I am pleased that the inquiry
OL,11,Fwill now finally be able to get under
OL,12,Fway."
OL,14,FMs Finucane said: "The establishment
OL,15,Fof this inquiry is a significant
OL,16,Fmoment in that long journey.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@EO]vD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773176766
OL,3,CTerms of reference for Pat Finucane
OL,4,Cinquiry published
OL,6,F"We welcome the publication of the
OL,7,Fterms of reference and the formal
OL,8,Fcommencement of the inquiry's work. My
OL,9,Ffamily and I will engage
OL,10,Fconstructively with the process and
OL,11,Fwill carefully consider the detail of
OL,12,Fthe terms that have been set out.
OL,14,F"It is essential that the chair and
OL,15,Fthe inquiry are fully independent and
OL,16,Ffree to follow the evidence wherever
OL,17,Fit leads. We expect that the inquiry
OL,18,Fwill conduct its work thoroughly,
OL,19,Ftransparently and in accordance with
OL,20,Fthe state's obligations under Article
OL,21,F2.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773176766
OL,3,CTerms of reference for Pat Finucane
OL,4,Cinquiry published
OL,6,F"Our focus remains, as it always has
OL,7,Fbeen, on establishing the full truth
OL,8,Fabout Pat's murder."
OL,10,FMr Benn said the terms of reference
OL,11,Fwere developed following formal
OL,12,Fconsultation with chair of the inquiry
OL,13,FSir Gary Hickinbottom, who had
OL,14,Fconsulted with the Finucane family
OL,15,F"who provided very helpful feedback
OL,16,Fand observations".
OL,18,FHe added: "I would like to thank Sir
OL,19,FGary and the Finucane family for their
OL,20,Fengagement throughout the process."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@TO]wD@AOUxD@QO]zD@KOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
