PN,44807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773176766
OL,3,CTerms of reference for Pat Finucane
OL,4,Cinquiry published
OL,6,FThe inquiry will have the power to
OL,7,Fcompel the production of documents and
OL,8,Fto summon witnesses to give evidence
OL,9,Fon oath.
OL,11,FSir Gary said he was "grateful" for
OL,12,Fthe announcement of the inquiry terms
OL,13,Fof reference and invited potential
OL,14,Fcore participants to apply.
OL,16,F"This is an important moment, as it
OL,17,Festablishes the inquiry on a formal
OL,18,Ffooting and allows us to begin our
OL,19,Fwork in earnest.
OL,26,@sD@VOUsD@_O]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773176766
OL,3,CTerms of reference for Pat Finucane
OL,4,Cinquiry published
OL,6,F"I wish to build momentum at this
OL,7,Fearly stage. I intend to fulfil my
OL,8,Fduties as chair as fairly, openly and
OL,9,Ftransparently as possible, operating
OL,10,Findependently from government and any
OL,11,Fother outside influence.
OL,13,F"I am keen for the inquiry to proceed
OL,14,Fat pace to fulfil its terms of
OL,15,Freference and with that in mind, I am
OL,16,Ftoday inviting anyone who feels they
OL,17,Fmay be entitled to be a core
OL,18,Fparticipant in this inquiry to apply
OL,19,Fto do so."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/9
